<subSubSection pageId="8" pageNumber="107" type="distribution">
<paragraph blockId="8.[136,1452,446,1481]" pageId="8" pageNumber="107">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,487,1130,1156]" pageId="8" pageNumber="107">Distribution and habitat:</emphasis>
—This Amazonian species is found in 
<collectingCountry box="[912,983,1130,1156]" name="Brazil" pageId="8" pageNumber="107">Brazil</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[993,1106,1130,1156]" name="Colombia" pageId="8" pageNumber="107">Colombia</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[1116,1209,1130,1156]" name="Ecuador" pageId="8" pageNumber="107">Ecuador</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingCountry box="[1261,1312,1131,1157]" name="Peru" pageId="8" pageNumber="107">Peru</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Judziewicz, E. J. &amp; Clark, L. G." pageId="8" pageNumber="107" pagination="80 - 99" refId="ref24854" refString="Judziewicz, E. J. &amp; Clark, L. G. (1993) The South American Species of Arthrostylidium (Poaceae: Bambusoideae: Bambuseae). Systematic Botany 18 (1): 80 - 99. https: // doi. org / 10.2307 / 2419790" type="journal article" year="1993">Judziewicz &amp; Clark 1993</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Vorontsova, M. S. &amp; Clark, L. G. &amp; Dransfield, J. &amp; Govaerts, R. &amp; Baker, W. J." box="[307,568,1166,1193]" pageId="8" pageNumber="107" refId="ref27897" refString="Vorontsova, M. S., Clark, L. G., Dransfield, J., Govaerts, R. &amp; Baker, W. J. (2016) World Checklist of Bamboos and Rattans. International Network for Bamboo and Rattan, Beijing, China, 446 pp." type="book" year="2016">
Vorontsova 
<emphasis box="[442,499,1166,1192]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="107">et al.</emphasis>
2016
</bibRefCitation>
). In 
<collectingCountry box="[618,689,1166,1192]" name="Brazil" pageId="8" pageNumber="107">Brazil</collectingCountry>
, it is registered in Amazonas state (
<bibRefCitation author="Viana, P. L." box="[1092,1225,1166,1192]" pageId="8" pageNumber="107" refId="ref27420" refString="Viana, P. L. (2020) Arthrostylidium in Flora do Brasil 2020, Jardim Botanico do Rio de Janeiro, Rio de Janeiro, Rio de Janeiro state, Brazil. Available from: http: // floradobrasil. jbrj. gov. br / reflora / floradobrasil / FB 86734 (accessed 9 October 2021)." type="url" year="2020">Viana 2020</bibRefCitation>
) and this is the first record for Pará state. This species occurs in wet lowland forests at elevations from 30 to 300 meters (
<bibRefCitation author="Judziewicz, E. J. &amp; Clark, L. G." pageId="8" pageNumber="107" pagination="80 - 99" refId="ref24854" refString="Judziewicz, E. J. &amp; Clark, L. G. (1993) The South American Species of Arthrostylidium (Poaceae: Bambusoideae: Bambuseae). Systematic Botany 18 (1): 80 - 99. https: // doi. org / 10.2307 / 2419790" type="journal article" year="1993">Judziewicz &amp; Clark 1993</bibRefCitation>
). In the Serra do Cachimbo, it was found in Open ombrophilous forest, along the Curuá rivers margins.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
