<emphasis box="[356,728,1274,1300]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="107">Arthrostylidium simpliciusculum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is the only species of the genus with the lemma midnerve prolonged into a scabrous awn 1.5–3(5) mm long (
<bibRefCitation author="Judziewicz, E. J. &amp; Clark, L. G." box="[713,1008,1310,1336]" pageId="8" pageNumber="107" pagination="80 - 99" refId="ref24854" refString="Judziewicz, E. J. &amp; Clark, L. G. (1993) The South American Species of Arthrostylidium (Poaceae: Bambusoideae: Bambuseae). Systematic Botany 18 (1): 80 - 99. https: // doi. org / 10.2307 / 2419790" type="journal article" year="1993">Judziewicz &amp; Clark 1993</bibRefCitation>
). It can be recognized by the culm leaf margins ciliate, with whitish trichomes, summit sparsely fimbriate, ca. 
<quantity box="[964,1053,1346,1373]" metricMagnitude="-4" metricUnit="m" metricValue="5.0" pageId="8" pageNumber="107" unit="mm" value="0.5">0.5 mm</quantity>
long, blades triangular-lanceolate, apex setose, tip 
<quantity box="[317,410,1382,1409]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="5.5" metricValueMax="6.0" metricValueMin="5.0" pageId="8" pageNumber="107" unit="mm" value="5.5" valueMax="6.0" valueMin="5.0">5–6 mm</quantity>
long and foliage leaf sheath glabrous except minutely pubescent at one margin, fimbriae ca. 
<quantity box="[136,201,1418,1445]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="5.0" pageId="8" pageNumber="107" unit="mm" value="5.0">5 mm</quantity>
long, ochraceous, and blades 10–14 × 
<quantity box="[634,741,1418,1445]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="7.5" metricValueMax="10.0" metricValueMin="5.0" pageId="8" pageNumber="107" unit="cm" value="0.75" valueMax="1.0" valueMin="0.5">0.5–1 cm</quantity>
, lanceolate, and glabrous on both surfaces, except 1–2 scabrous marginal nerves. To distinguish this from 
<taxonomicName box="[604,946,1454,1480]" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Arthrostylidium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="8" pageNumber="107" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="cachimboense">
<emphasis box="[604,946,1454,1480]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="107">Arthrostylidium cachimboense</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, see comments under that species.
</paragraph>
